  "description": "A close-up, low-angle shot depicts a single, delicate feather resting on dark, coarse sand. The feather is light beige with intricate barbs, sharply defined against the granular texture of the sand. Light rakes across the sand creating strong shadows, highlighting the contours of the sand dunes. The sand itself appears volcanic or basaltic, being a dark grey/black. Focus is sharp on the feather, and the background subtly blurs. The scene evokes a feeling of stillness and subtle beauty.",
